# Day 7 - Machine Learning Development Life Cycle (MLDLC)

## What is MLDLC?

MLDLC is the step-by-step process of building a Machine Learning project.

It helps in creating accurate and reliable ML models.

## Steps of MLDLC

### 1. Data Collection

Gather data from different sources.

### 2. Data Preparation

Clean and organize the data.

### 3. Data Exploration

Understand patterns and relationships in the data.

### 4. Model Building

Select and train a Machine Learning model.

### 5. Model Evaluation

Check the performance of the model.

### 6. Model Deployment

Use the model in a real-world application.

### 7. Monitoring

Track the model and update it when needed.

## Workflow

Data Collection → Data Preparation → Data Exploration → Model Building → Model Evaluation → Deployment → Monitoring

## Real Example

House Price Prediction:

* Collect house data
* Clean the data
* Train the model
* Test accuracy
* Deploy the model
* Monitor performance

## Important Points

* MLDLC is a complete ML project process.
* Data preparation is an important step.
* Model evaluation checks model quality.
* Deployment makes the model available to users.
* Monitoring helps maintain performance.

## One-Line Summary

MLDLC is the complete process of collecting data, building a model, deploying it, and monitoring its performance.
